<p><strong>1. Develop Sincere Yearning For God</strong></p>

<p><strong>2. Loyalty and Dedication to God and to the Guru Whose Path One Chooses.</strong></p>

<p><strong>3. Behave in a way to Inspire Others Towards God</strong></p>

<p><strong>4. Strive Constantly for Humility</strong></p>

<p><strong>5. Set Aside Time Every Day for Meditation</strong></p>

<p>Reference:
<em>These are taken from a Chapter Qualities of a Devotee by Gyan Mata ~ Only Love</em></p>
